; countdown.anal — counts down from 5 to 1, printing each on its own line.
;
; The counter lives on the stack. Before entering DILATE we push the
; loop condition (counter > 0) so DILATE has something to pop. Each
; iteration we DUP-then-DISCHARGE so the printed value is consumed
; without losing the counter, decrement, and re-push the condition.

ANAL "countdown" VERSION 1

PUSH 5

DUP PUSH 0 GT

DILATE
  DUP
  DISCHARGE
  PUSH 1
  SUB
  DUP PUSH 0 GT
CONSTRICT

POP
